author: craigmcc
msg: Initial commit of a command link component (<s:commandLink>) that is
analogous to the standard <h:commandLink> but works when inside a
Struts <s:form> component.  Most JSF implementations have dependencies
between the renderers for their Form and Command Link components, so it
was necessary to make hyperlinks that submit a form available when using
The associated system integration test checks for the presence of the
appropriate generated elements, but HtmlUnit 1.2.3's JavaScript support
does not seem to be capable of actually executing the generated "onclick"
